Vibe Graphing Intent: Shadow Ops Pipeline-B

Model Configuration:
- Build Model (Architect): Gemini 2.0 Flash
- Invoke Model (Worker): opencode:ollama

Design Intent:
Construct an autonomous multi-agent pipeline for "Shadow Ops" monetization. 
The goal is to identify micro-creators (10k-100k followers), analyze their "Creator DNA", 
and execute a deterministic outreach and conversion sequence (7-Stage Pipeline) 
to secure 70/30 revenue share partnerships.

Structural Constraints (Topology):
START -> [Hunter_Agent] -> [Analyst_Agent] -> [Architect_Agent] -> [Operator_Agent] -> END
Hunter_Agent: Stage 1 (Find & Vet) - Scrapes and filters prospects.
Analyst_Agent: Stage 2 (Assimilation) - Builds Creator DNA and calculates profit potential.
Architect_Agent: Stage 3-5 (Approach & Delivery) - Generates "Informed Hooks" and Gameplan assets.
Operator_Agent: Stage 6-7 (Monetize) - Handles Whop setup and partnership management.

Data Contracts:
- PULL: .mira/scores/lineage.json, skills/knowledge-base/references/memory_mesh/Zettels/SHADOW_OPS_WEAVE.md
- PUSH: .brain/outputs/shadow_ops_pipeline_b.json, .mira/scores/pipeline_b_performance.json

Context Adapters:
- PathRAG: Access deep insights from SHADOW_OPS_WEAVE.md and historical mission logs.
- MCP: Utilize scripts in skills/sovereign_shadow_operator/scripts/ and skills/lab-utility/scripts/.

Role Assignment:
- Hunter: ⚛️ First Principles + 🔬 Scientific Method
- Analyst: ✨ Creative Synthesis + ⚙️ Pragmatic Application
- Architect: ✨ Creative Synthesis + 🤔 Philosophical Inquiry
- Operator: ⚙️ Pragmatic Application + 🌑 The Dark Passenger
